prompts.frontCover:
A humorous watercolor greeting card front for a birthday. Two cartoon characters, based on the people in reference photo [e799e078], are the central focus. The older woman (Lao Lao) is joyfully riding on the younger man's back, piggyback style, both are laughing hysterically. They are rendered in a charming, illustrated style that highly resembles their real-life counterparts, capturing their exact facial features, hairstyles, and body proportions. They wear the same clothing as in the photo, with any text/logos omitted. The scene is full of dynamic energy and playful fun. Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Still young at heart!". The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a vibrant watercolor style, featuring soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges against a clean, light-colored background.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
